name: Dr. Matt and Debra St. John
text: We love this place and selectively buy meat from here on am increasingly regular basis.   We have eaten steaks and chicken  from here across the country while traveling, and prefer the meat from here over most any butcher in the US.   Here are a couple of filets we bought yesterday and grilled using Tony's special seasoning mix, Amish Butter, fried mushrooms with Urbani Truffles and parmesan cheese,  and homemade potato chips.   You could cut the filet with a knife.

name: Susan Mackey
text: We LOVE this place!  Great meat, great prices, friendly staff.

name: Elizabeth Crabtree
text: Excellent meat, courteous, knowledgeable and helpful staff! We love Michelle.

name: Barbecue AnytimeAnyplace
text: Good old fashioned meat market with great cuts. You’ll be proud to be a carnivore. Friendly folks too.

name: Tami Sparks
text: Friendly and professional.   Great quality and selection of meat!

name: Hannah T
text: They have the best meat around! My husband and I have bought our meats from here since we moved to Alabama. We have even brought our family and friends here to purchase meat and everyone loved it!! Not to mention, the lady in the front is the sweetest person ever!!

name: Jimmy Mccord
text: Best steaks in town a level above any other place

name: Randy Voiles
text: Good quality meat at reasonable prices, and great people

name: Martha Barnett
text: Love this place! Good meats at reasonable prices. The butcher cuts your meat to order.

text: The Maet is cut just right!!!
